            <lg xml:id="TK34">
<l>maṉattukkaṇ mācila ṉāta laṉaittaṟa</l>
<l>ṉākula nīra piṟa</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As long as one is unblemished in mind, so long is there dharma;</l>
<l>all else just a ruckus.</l>
